                <h2>Responsibilities Variation <span class='clicktooltip' title='Select "Yes" and include details if you have a written Variation of Responsibilities agreement in place during the reporting year with, for example, non-standard percentage weights for research, teaching and service.'>&#9432;</span></h2>
                Is there a formal Variance of Responsibilities Agreement in place as per Articles 7.02.2 and 13.1 of the <a href='https://cloudfront.ualberta.ca/-/media/hrs/my-employment/agreements/faculty-agreement.pdf' target='_blank'>Faculty Agreement</a>?
